{"id":94,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":94,"title":"D&C 90","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 90"],[".studyIntro",["i","Revelation to Joseph Smith the Prophet, given at Kirtland, Ohio, March 8, 1833. This revelation is a continuing step in the establishment of the First Presidency (see the",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/81.head"},"heading to section 81"],"); as a consequence thereof, the counselors mentioned were ordained on March 18, 1833."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.1-5"},"1–5"],", The keys of the kingdom are committed to Joseph Smith and through him to the Church;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.6-7"},"6–7"],", Sidney Rigdon and Frederick G. Williams are to serve in the First Presidency;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.8-11"},"8–11"],", The gospel is to be preached to the nations of Israel, to the Gentiles, and to the Jews, every man hearing in his own tongue;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.12-18"},"12–18"],", Joseph Smith and his counselors are to set the Church in order;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.19-37"},"19–37"],", Various individuals are counseled by the Lord to walk uprightly and serve in His kingdom."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.1","order":"06.05.090.11641"},["b","1"],"Thus saith the Lord, verily, verily I say unto you my son, thy sins are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"forgiven"],"thee, according to thy petition, for thy prayers and the prayers of thy brethren have come up into my ears."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.2","order":"06.05.090.11642"},["b","2"],"Therefore, thou art blessed from henceforth that bear the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"keys"],"of the kingdom given unto you; which",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"kingdom"],"is coming forth for the last time."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.3","order":"06.05.090.11643"},["b","3"],"Verily I say unto you, the keys of this",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"kingdom"],"shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"never"],"be taken from you, while thou art in the world, neither in the world to come;"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.4","order":"06.05.090.11644"},["b","4"],"Nevertheless, through you shall the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"oracles"],"be given to another, yea, even unto the church."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.5","order":"06.05.090.11645"},["b","5"],"And all they who receive the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"oracles"],"of God, let them beware how they hold them lest they are accounted as a light thing, and are brought under condemnation thereby, and stumble and fall when the storms descend, and the winds blow, and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"rains"],"descend, and beat upon their house."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.6","order":"06.05.090.11646"},["b","6"],"And again, verily I say unto thy brethren, Sidney Rigdon and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"Frederick G. Williams"],", their sins are forgiven them also, and they are accounted as",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"equal"],"with thee in holding the keys of this last kingdom;"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.7","order":"06.05.090.11647"},["b","7"],"As also through your administration the keys of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"school"],"of the prophets, which I have commanded to be organized;"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.8","order":"06.05.090.11648"},["b","8"],"That thereby they may be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"perfected"],"in their ministry for the salvation of Zion, and of the nations of Israel, and of the Gentiles, as many as will believe;"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.9","order":"06.05.090.11649"},["b","9"],"That through your administration they may receive the word, and through their administration the word may go forth unto the ends of the earth, unto the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"Gentiles"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"first"],", and then, behold, and lo, they shall turn unto the Jews."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.10","order":"06.05.090.11650"},["b","10"],"And then cometh the day when the arm of the Lord shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"revealed"],"in power in convincing the nations, the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"heathen"],"nations, the house of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"Joseph"],", of the gospel of their salvation."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.11","order":"06.05.090.11651"},["b","11"],"For it shall come to pass in that day, that every man shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"hear"],"the fulness of the gospel in his own tongue, and in his own",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"language"],", through those who are",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"ordained"],"unto this",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_11d"},"power"],", by the administration of the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_11e"},"Comforter"],", shed forth upon them for the",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_11f"},"revelation"],"of Jesus Christ."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.12","order":"06.05.090.11652"},["b","12"],"And now, verily I say unto you, I give unto you a commandment that you continue in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"ministry"],"and presidency."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.13","order":"06.05.090.11653"},["b","13"],"And when you have finished the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"translation"],"of the prophets, you shall from thenceforth",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"preside"],"over the affairs of the church and the school;"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.14","order":"06.05.090.11654"},["b","14"],"And from time to time, as shall be manifested by the Comforter, receive",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"revelations"],"to unfold the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"mysteries"],"of the kingdom;"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.15","order":"06.05.090.11655"},["b","15"],"And set in order the churches, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"study"],"and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"learn"],", and become acquainted with all good books, and with",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"languages"],", tongues, and people."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.16","order":"06.05.090.11656"},["b","16"],"And this shall be your business and mission in all your lives, to preside in council, and set in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"order"],"all the affairs of this church and kingdom."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.17","order":"06.05.090.11657"},["b","17"],"Be not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"ashamed"],", neither confounded; but be admonished in all your high-mindedness and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"pride"],", for it bringeth a snare upon your souls."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.18","order":"06.05.090.11658"},["b","18"],"Set in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"order"],"your houses; keep",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"slothfulness"],"and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"uncleanness"],"far from you."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.19","order":"06.05.090.11659"},["b","19"],"Now, verily I say unto you, let there be a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"place"],"provided, as soon as it is possible, for the family of thy counselor and scribe, even Frederick G. Williams."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.20","order":"06.05.090.11660"},["b","20"],"And let mine aged servant,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"Joseph Smith, Sen."],", continue with his family upon the place where he now lives; and let it not be sold until the mouth of the Lord shall name."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.21","order":"06.05.090.11661"},["b","21"],"And let my counselor, even",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"Sidney Rigdon"],", remain where he now resides until the mouth of the Lord shall name."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.22","order":"06.05.090.11662"},["b","22"],"And let the bishop search diligently to obtain an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"agent"],", and let him be a man who has got",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"riches"],"in store—a man of God, and of strong faith—"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.23","order":"06.05.090.11663"},["b","23"],"That thereby he may be enabled to discharge every debt; that the storehouse of the Lord may not be brought into disrepute before the eyes of the people."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.24","order":"06.05.090.11664"},["b","24"],"Search",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"diligently"],",",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"pray"],"always, and be believing, and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_24c"},"all"],"things shall work together for your good, if ye walk uprightly and remember the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_24d"},"covenant"],"wherewith ye have covenanted one with another."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.25","order":"06.05.090.11665"},["b","25"],"Let your families be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"small"],", especially mine aged servant Joseph Smith’s, Sen., as pertaining to those who do not belong to your families;"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.26","order":"06.05.090.11666"},["b","26"],"That those things that are provided for you, to bring to pass my work, be not taken from you and given to those that are not worthy—"],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.27","order":"06.05.090.11667"},["b","27"],"And thereby you be hindered in accomplishing those things which I have commanded you."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.28","order":"06.05.090.11668"},["b","28"],"And again, verily I say unto you, it is my will that my handmaid Vienna Jaques should receive",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"money"],"to bear her expenses, and go up unto the land of Zion;"],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.29","order":"06.05.090.11669"},["b","29"],"And the residue of the money may be consecrated unto me, and she be rewarded in mine own due time."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.30","order":"06.05.090.11670"},["b","30"],"Verily I say unto you, that it is meet in mine eyes that she should go up unto the land of Zion, and receive an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"inheritance"],"from the hand of the bishop;"],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.31","order":"06.05.090.11671"},["b","31"],"That she may settle down in peace inasmuch as she is faithful, and not be idle in her days from thenceforth."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.32","order":"06.05.090.11672"},["b","32"],"And behold, verily I say unto you, that ye shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"write"],"this commandment, and say unto your brethren in Zion, in love greeting, that I have called you also to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_32b"},"preside"],"over Zion in mine own due time."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.33","order":"06.05.090.11673"},["b","33"],"Therefore, let them cease wearying me concerning this matter."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.34","order":"06.05.090.11674"},["b","34"],"Behold, I say unto you that your brethren in Zion begin to repent, and the angels rejoice over them."],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.35","order":"06.05.090.11675"},["b","35"],"Nevertheless, I am not well pleased with many things; and I am not well pleased with my servant",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_35a"},"William E. McLellin"],", neither with my servant Sidney Gilbert; and the bishop also, and others have many things to repent of."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.36","order":"06.05.090.11676"},["b","36"],"But verily I say unto you, that I, the Lord, will contend with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_36a"},"Zion"],", and plead with her strong ones, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_36b"},"chasten"],"her until she overcomes and is",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_36c"},"clean"],"before me."],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.37","order":"06.05.090.11677"},["b","37"],"For she shall not be removed out of her place. I, the Lord, have spoken it. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.1a","order":"06.05.090.11678"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/forgive"},"TG Forgive"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.2a","order":"06.05.090.11680"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-keys-of"},"TG Priesthood, Keys of"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.2b","order":"06.05.090.11682"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-prophecies-about"},"TG Jesus Christ, Prophecies about"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.3a","order":"06.05.090.11684"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/21.43"},"Matt. 21:43"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/65.2"},"D&C 65:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.3b","order":"06.05.090.11686"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/43.3.3-4"},"D&C 43:3 (3–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.17"},"84:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/122.9"},"122:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/124.130"},"124:130"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.4a","order":"06.05.090.11688"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/7.38"},"Acts 7:38"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/3.2"},"Rom. 3:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/5.12"},"Heb. 5:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/124.39,126"},"D&C 124:39, 126"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophets-mission-of"},"TG Prophets, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.5a","order":"06.05.090.11690"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/7.38"},"Acts 7:38"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophets-rejection-of"},"TG Prophets, Rejection of"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.5b","order":"06.05.090.11692"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/7.25"},"Matt. 7:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.6a","order":"06.05.090.11694"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/92.1"},"D&C 92:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.6b","order":"06.05.090.11696"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.22.3-23"},"D&C 35:22 (3–23)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/81.1.1-7"},"81:1 (1–7)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/107.24.22-24"},"107:24 (22–24)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.7a","order":"06.05.090.11698"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.127"},"D&C 88:127"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.8a","order":"06.05.090.11700"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/eph/4.12.11-13"},"Eph. 4:12 (11–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptu